{"name":"Prism of Ambiguity","type":"misc","img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/prism.png","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.6ce2K9i7cVe9Ikb6"}},"_id":"0C6jqjKk87XZ7hf6","system":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>An external light source and a Presence DR10 test are needed to activate the prism. Its light may shine on up to two creatures healing d6 HP. For the next hour one of them lowers all test DRs by -2. If the test is failed they suffer d4 damage and their armor or a weapon is destroyed. You can use the prism twice per day.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"carried":true,"price":0,"quantity":1},"ownership":{"default":0,"8TrFu59c1zX6K3pu":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"morkborg","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1684780211601,"lastModifiedBy":"LYF9zR8SvB0h2e6R"}}
{"name":"Thorns of Comprehension","type":"misc","img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/crown-of-thorns.png","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.s5wIdYpzDJlwtz2i"}},"_id":"4EIomHdGDrtWC3en","system":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>When worn, thorns pierce your flesh (d2 damage) and you Perceive All (-4DR to your next test and ignore the next two attacks to hit you as you weave aside). To regain the effect you must crown yourself anew. The damage steps up by one each time (d2 to d4 to d6 etc), until after a night&rsquo;s rest.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"carried":true,"price":0,"quantity":1},"ownership":{"default":0,"8TrFu59c1zX6K3pu":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"morkborg","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1684780279320,"lastModifiedBy":"LYF9zR8SvB0h2e6R"}}
{"name":"Sash of the Stylite","type":"misc","img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/sash.png","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.AzhdDJS1CQxhTGnB"}},"_id":"6I6NPS2jVKlza0B5","system":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>The MIND controls the body! Nothing is good or bad but thinking makes it so including calories and protein. Wearing this belt means you feel no hunger and only need to drink water to regain HP when resting. Wearing it for more than d4 days causes you to collapse. It takes a day to regain its power.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"carried":true,"price":0,"quantity":1},"ownership":{"default":0,"8TrFu59c1zX6K3pu":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"morkborg","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1684780224274,"lastModifiedBy":"LYF9zR8SvB0h2e6R"}}
{"name":"Marked by Obscurity","type":"feat","img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/forlorn_philosopher.png","data":{"description":"<p>An ever-shifting Tablet of Ochre Obscurity is tattooed on your flesh. Roll each morning which tablet it is. The tablet can only be used once per day but automatically succeeds.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"8TrFu59c1zX6K3pu":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.eXV8K2Em6Cnti6YE"}},"_id":"7BbBce8M7v2SCEVS"}
{"_id":"L9Vwzbx5o0OMdJm0","name":"Forlorn Philosopher","type":"class","img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/forlorn_philosopher.png","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.KPgmjbh5vEtF9Hu8"}},"system":{"abilities":"<p>Mental Focus, roll 3d6+2 Presence. Too Much Reading! Roll 3d6-2 Strength. Ruthless Inquisition: test Presence DR 14 to tear through others&rsquo; deceptions and delusions. Enough of these LIES! Roll d6 on the weapon table and d2 on the armor table. You begin with one Tablet of Ochre Obscurity and one of the following:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>THORNS OF COMPREHENSION</li>\n<li>HEGELIAN OWL</li>\n<li>PRISM OF AMBIGUITY</li>\n<li>FLUTE OF TOSK</li>\n<li>BASH OF THE STYLITE</li>\n<li>MARKED BY OBSCURITY</li>\n</ol>","armorTableDie":"1d2","description":"The road an unreasoning maze, every temple soaked in blood, each destination drenched in gloom; you once thought that cold analysis might tame Fate itself, now that dream of reason has decayed to shifting madness and only the cold remains.","omenDie":"1d4","startingAgility":"3d6","startingHitPoints":"1d4","startingItems":"morkborg.class-forlorn-philosopher,Ruthless Inquisition","startingPresence":"3d6+2","startingRolls":"morkborg.rolls-forlorn-philosopher,Forlorn Philosopher Items,1\nmorkborg.random-tables,The Tablets of Ochre Obscurity,1\nmorkborg.rolls-forlorn-philosopher,The Roots of your Dejection,1\nmorkborg.rolls-forlorn-philosopher,The dejection of your Roots,1","startingSilver":"1d6*10","startingStrength":"3d6-2","startingToughness":"3d6","weaponTableDie":"1d6"},"ownership":{"default":0,"8TrFu59c1zX6K3pu":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"morkborg","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1684780924427,"lastModifiedBy":"LYF9zR8SvB0h2e6R"}}
